overview: The user initiated a request for a complete aesthetic overhaul of
  their sleep questionnaire application, expressing dissatisfaction with its
  current generic appearance. The assistant began by conducting an in-depth
  review of the app's styling across various components and global
  configurations. Following this analysis, which highlighted issues like a bland
  color palette and lack of visual interest, the assistant implemented a new,
  calming sleep-themed color palette in the global CSS. Subsequently, the main
   component was significantly enhanced with a more visually
  appealing layout, an improved progress indicator, a richer card header
  featuring a subtle pattern, and decorative background elements to create a
  more immersive and professional user experience. The navigation buttons were
  also refined to align with the new aesthetic.
